me.name: Chris Jennings
me.bio: In my artistic journey, I’ve discovered a profound fascination with the harmonious interplay between the natural world and the structured order of geometry. My digital collages represent a creative exploration where I seamlessly blend the intricate details captured in photographs from nature with meticulously constructed geometric shapes derived from the colours within these images.
